<table-row><table-column preferred-width="12.03cm"><paragraph-text type="body">Separating solids from solids by subjecting their mixture to gas currents while the mixtures are supported by sieves, screens, or like mechanical elements and material is passing through the sieve, screen or the like</paragraph-text></table-column><table-column preferred-width="3.01cm"><paragraph-text type="body"><class-ref scheme="cpc">B07B4/08</class-ref></paragraph-text></table-column></table-row></table></section-body></informative-references></references></definition-item>
